info.name: Sunday 5-Drawer Tallboy
info.description: The Sunday 5-drawer tallboy is a perfect storage piece to add to your child's room - with its antique rustic look it creates a charming home feel. Style with the ABC chest and one of our Sunday beds for a nostalgic look bedroom. Crafted from recycled old Pine timber, the Sunday tallboy features 5 storage drawers finished off with quaint rope handle drawers.
